<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَيَنْتَفِي الوَلَدُ بِنَفْيِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ أَتَتْ زَوْجَتُهُ بِوَلَدٍ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- بَعْدَ نِصْفِ سَنَةٍ مُنْذُ أَمْكَنَ اجْتِمَاعُهُ بِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- أَوْ لِدُونِ أَرْبَعِ سِنِينَ مُنْذُ أَبَانَهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَلَوِ ابْنَ عَشْرٍ:</span> لَحِقَهُ نَسَبُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَلَا يُحْكَمُ بِبُلُوغِهِ مَعَ شَكٍّ فِيهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَمَنْ أَعْتَقَ، أَوْ بَاعَ مَنْ أَقَرَّ بِوَطْئِهَا،<span class="c5"> فَوَلَدَتْ لِدُونِ نِصْفِ سَنَةٍ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- لَحِقَهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- والبَيْعُ بَاطِلٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>